<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-94-0619 </DOCNO><TEXT>In the electric steel plant of the VEB Stahl- und Walzwerk Hennigsdorfthree 65 (metric)-tons UHP are furnaces with water-cooled furnace casingsand covers are in operation. To these two four-strand billet castersare directly followed. To fully utilize the plant-technological and theeconomic advantages of the equipment automation systems for a computer-aidedprocess control have been developed. In the paper the automation systems,the instrument configuration applied, the software, and the economicefficiency are dealt with.</TEXT></DOC>